      <title>中国散户投资者对股票的热情迅速消退</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-retail-investor-sours-quickly-stocks-2025-01-14/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日内交易员陆德龙对中国股市反弹的乐观情绪在今年第一周迅速消失，当时，距离他为受北京刺激承诺推动的股市上涨做准备仅仅三个月，他却被迫抛售股票并计算亏损。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-retail-investor-sours-quickly-stocks-2025-01-14/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 02:32:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
